## Supplementary Figure 8D-GSEA Enrichment Across Epithelial Populations

Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA) of epithelial populations across developmental and transitional cell states.

### Workflow

- Ranked gene lists were generated from differential expression analyses.
- Gene Set Enrichment Analysis was performed using predefined biological gene sets.
- Normalized Enrichment Scores (NES) were calculated.
- Enrichment patterns were compared across epithelial populations.

### Software

- R
- clusterProfiler
- fgsea
- ggplot2
